OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A grandmother cleared of fraud charges 
OL,6, after spending seven years with the    
OL,7, allegations hanging over her, says     
OL,8, every part of her life has been        
OL,9, "destroyed".                           
OL,11,FKrista Brown, who was arrested in 2017 
OL,12,Fand charged three years later, says the
OL,13,Fstress of not knowing when her trial   
OL,14,Fmight be scheduled has affected her    
OL,15,F"financially, mentally, physically".   
OL,17,FThe 51-year-old, who denied the        
OL,18,Fcharges, says she closed her business  
OL,19,Fand had to rely on benefits.           
